(27, 1, '2011-06-07 23:57:58', '2011-06-08 03:57:58', '<strong>Green Street Studios has the following spaces available </strong>\n\n<strong>for rehearsals, classes, and performances:</strong>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1712" align="alignright" width="300" caption="Studio #1                                                                          Photo by Liza Voll Photography"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-1712 " src="http://greenstreetstudios.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/GSS-by-Liza-Voll-7-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" />[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Studio #1</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nBlack fully sprung marley floor with full length mirrors along one wall, windows along one wall, and a skylight. 2,500 square feet, (40 X 60). This studio also functions as a performance space.\n<br />\n<a title="Rent Space" href="http://greenstreetstudios.org/rentals/rent-space/" target="_blank">RENT Studio #1 for your rehearsal, workshop, or performance</a>\n<br />\nLocal companies that rehearse at Green Street:\n\nContrapose Dance, EgoArt, Inc., Danny McCusker and Dancers, Luminarium Dance, and more...\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Studio #2</strong>\n\n[caption id="attachment_1713" align="alignright" width="300" caption="Studio #2                                                                         Photo by Liza Voll Photography"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-1713" src="http://greenstreetstudios.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/GSS-by-Liza-Voll-15-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300" />[/caption]\n\n<strong></strong>\nGrey fully sprung floor with full length mirrors along one wall and a skylight. 1,500 square foot, (35 X 40)\n<br />\n<a title="Rent Space" href="http://greenstreetstudios.org/rentals/rent-space/" target="_blank">RENT Studio #2 for your rehearsal or workshop</a>\n<br />\n*Our facilities also include a dressing room and three bathrooms.* <strong>PLEASE NOTE: </strong>due to the marley flooring, NO STREET SHOES OR HEELED SHOES are allowed in the studios.\n\n<a href="http://greenstreetstudios.org/?page_id=176" target="_blank">Rent Space</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nIf you are a dancer/teacher and are interested in renting space in our studios for rehearsing, teaching classes or workshops, or performing, please email all requests to <a href="mailto:scheduling@greenstreetstudios.org" target="_blank">scheduling@greenstreetstudios.org</a> or leave a voicemail in the Space Rental Requests mailbox at 617-864-3191. For more info click <a title="Rent Space" href="http://greenstreetstudios.org/rentals/rent-space/" target="_blank">here</a>.', 'Rentals', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'rentals', '', '', '2011-06-07 23:57:58', '2011-06-08 03:57:58', '', 0, 'http://greenstreetstudios.org/wordpress/?page_id=27', 3, 'page', '', 0),
