(34, 1, '2011-06-07 23:59:12', '2011-06-08 03:59:12', '<strong>Volunteer with us!</strong>\n\n<em>**GSS seeks enthusiastic and responsible work study students for the Spring/Summer. Cleaning and office shifts may be available; 3 month commitment required. Please contact <a href="mailto:info@greenstreetstudios.org" target="_blank">info@greenstreetstudios.org</a> if interested.</em>\n<br />\n[caption id="attachment_482" align="alignright" width="199" caption="Photo by Liza Voll Photography"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-482 " src="http://greenstreetstudios.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/DSC1293-1111-199x300.jpg" alt="" width="199" height="300" />[/caption]\n\nGreen Street Studios thrives upon the help and support of our volunteers. There are many ways to get involved in your local dance community through GSS including workstudy in exchange for classes. Please contact us at <strong>617-864-3191</strong> or email\n<a href="mailto:info@greenstreetstudios.org" target="_blank">info@greenstreetstudios.org</a> if you are interested in volunteering.\n<br />\nThank you to all of our wonderful past and present volunteers!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><a href="http://greenstreetstudios.org/?page_id=37" target="_blank">Become a Member!</a></strong> 2012 Members receive special ticket rates to events, rehearsal discounts, and more.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Donate!</strong>\n\nAs a small non-profit, GSS is always looking for donations from our generous supporters. If you''d like to donate money, we''d like to encourage you to become a member or sponsor us. We are always looking for people who can donate their time by volunteering with Green Street Studios. In addition, we are currently looking for the following donations:\n<br />\n- Stereo/audio equipment\n\n- New, comfortable folding chairs for the Theatre\n\n- Resources and capital for building an Elevator\n\n- New Carpeting\n\n- Video projector\n\n&nbsp;\n\nGreen Street Studios is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization', 'Get Involved', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'get-involved', '', '', '2011-06-07 23:59:12', '2011-06-08 03:59:12', '', 0, 'http://greenstreetstudios.org/wordpress/?page_id=34', 4, 'page', '', 0),
(37, 1, '2011-06-07 23:59:33', '2011-06-08 03:59:33', '[caption id="attachment_921" align="alignright" width="199" caption="Photo by Liza Voll Photography"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-527" src="http://greenstreetstudios.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/DSC1350-371-199x300.jpg" alt="" width="199" height="300" />[/caption]\n\n<strong>Green Street announces our Annual Membership Drive</strong>.\n\nSupport your local non-profit by becoming a 2012 Member! Please read our <a href="http://greenstreetstudios.smalls.cc/files/2011/06/GSS-Membership-Letter-2012.pdf" target="_blank">letter</a> with highlights from our 2011 season and exciting plans for 2012! Any donation amount is welcome. Donate today! Download the <a href="http://greenstreetstudios.smalls.cc/files/2011/11/GSS-Member-Form-20121.pdf" target="_blank">GSS Member Form 2012</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<em>Membership Benefits Include:</em>\n- Email Newsletters\n- Advance notice of special GSS events\n- Members'' discount to select performances (plus all GSS produced events)\n- Members'' discount to GSS sponsored master classes\n* Artist Members receive all of the above, plus discounted rehearsal space Monday-Friday from 9-5pm, plus one-time use of our mailing list.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nMembership Tiers:\nStudent Friend: $35\nFriend of Green Street: $50-$99\nProduction Partner: $100-$499\nSponsor: $500-$9999\nAngel: $1000 and up\n\nOR\n\nArtist Member: $150\nArtist Members receive a discounted rehearsal rate Monday through Friday from 9-5 and access to our mailing list for your dance even once per year.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nDonate today! Please download the <a href="http://greenstreetstudios.smalls.cc/files/2011/11/GSS-Member-Form-20121.pdf" target="_blank">GSS Member Form 2012</a> and mail it in with your payment to 185 Green Street, Cambridge, MA 02139\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Green Street Studios is a non-profit organization under the 501(c)(3) ruling. All donations are tax-deductible to the full extent of the law.\n\nThank you for being part of our community and for your support!\n\n&nbsp;', 'Membership', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'membership', '', '', '2011-06-07 23:59:33', '2011-06-08 03:59:33', '', 34, 'http://greenstreetstudios.org/wordpress/?page_id=37', 1, 'page', '', 0),
