(1734, 1, '2012-04-15 17:15:24', '2012-04-15 17:15:24', 'Green Street Studios is proud to be the home of <a href="http://www.bostonpercussivedance.com" target="_blank">Boston Percussive Dance</a>!\n\n&nbsp;\n\nFounded by tap dancer <a title="http://www.juliaontap.com/" href="http://www.juliaontap.com/" target="_blank">Julia Boynton</a> and Irish step dancer <a title="http://www.KieranJordan.com/" href="http://www.kieranjordan.com/" target="_blank">Kieran Jordan</a>, this new studio has been created as a home base for tap, Irish step, and other forms of percussive dance. Our studio features a new floor from Wooden Kiwi Productions, made of Rosco sprung panels, and a non-slip Duron surface that produces crisp clear sound. Come try it out! The studio is available for classes, workshops, rehearsals and events. For rentals or other information, contact <a title="mailto:jb@juliaontap.com?subject=studio rental" href="mailto:jb@juliaontap.com?subject=studio%20rental" target="_blank">Julia</a> or <a title="mailto:kieranjordandancers@gmail.com?subject=studio rental" href="mailto:kieranjordandancers@gmail.com?subject=studio%20rental" target="_blank">Kieran</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nBoston Percussive Dance is located at 185 Green Street in Central Square, Cambridge — the heart of the Boston dance community. Our space is inside Green Street Studios (Studio #3). Visit our website at <a title="http://www.bostonpercussivedance.com" href="http://www.bostonpercussivedance.com/" target="_blank">www.bostonpercussivedance.com</a>\n<br />\n[caption id="attachment_1732" align="aligncenter" width="717" caption="Boston Percussive Dance                                                                                                                                                                                       Photo by Liz Voll Photography"]<img class=" wp-image-1732 " src="http://greenstreetstudios.smalls.cc/files/2011/06/Studio3_Panorama-Liza-Voll-1024x306.jpg" alt="" width="717" height="214" />[/caption] ', 'Boston Percussive Dance', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'boston-percussive-dance', '', '', '2012-04-15 17:15:24', '2012-04-15 17:15:24', '', 1556, 'http://greenstreetstudios.org/?page_id=1734', 0, 'page', '', 0),
