(2015, 1, '2012-05-05 13:41:00', '2012-05-05 13:41:00', '<div>Following the formal reception, Boston Percussive Dance will host an after-party in studio 3, with DJ music, impromptu percussive dance performances,  live Irish music, and more. Come dance, mingle, and unwind!</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>The after-party is included in the $50 and $100 tickets. Separate $30 tickets for the party will be available online and at the door on Saturday, May 12th.</div>', 'After the Gala: Reception and after-party!!!!!!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'after-the-gala-reception-and-after-party', '', '', '2012-05-05 13:41:00', '2012-05-05 13:41:00', '', 0, 'http://greenstreetstudios.org/?p=2015', 0, 'post', '', 0),
