(2323, 1, '2012-07-08 04:06:57', '2012-07-08 04:06:57', 'Jimena Bermejo Kieran Jordan Abbie Katz Annie Kloppenberg Toni Matsu David Parker Birute Regine Marcus Schulkind Donna Wabrek Jimena Bermejo Jimena Bermejo was born in Mexico City holds an MFA in Studio for Interrelated Media from The Massachusetts College of Art and Design and BFA in Dance from The Boston Conservatory. Jimena has performed with Spencer/Colton, Marcus Schulkind, Kate Digby, Ego Art Inc., Kelli Edwards, Lorraine Chapman The Company, Caitlin Corbett Dance Company, Sarah Slifer and as a guest dancer with David Parker and The Bang Group. Along with performing Jimena continues to teach, choreograph and create video/performance pieces. Along with performing Jimena continues to teach, choreograph and create video/performance pieces, Jimena is a dance professor at The College of The Holy Cross and Suffolk University. Kieran Jordan Kieran Jordan is a performer, teacher, and choreographer of Irish dance, and co-founder/director of Boston Percussive Dance. With more than 30 years of experience in Irish dance, Kieran’s unique approach marries deep-rooted traditions with contemporary innovations. She has collaborated with many of New England’s finest traditional musicians, and has toured as a solo dancer and presented her choreography throughout North America and Europe. Kieran has been teaching in the Boston area since…', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2323', '', '', '2012-07-08 04:06:57', '2012-07-08 04:06:57', '', 47, 'http://greenstreetstudios.smalls.cc/2012/07/08/2323/', 36, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0);
