(2334, 1, '2012-07-08 04:07:00', '2012-07-08 04:07:00', 'Green Street Studios (GSS) is a laboratory for dance in the Boston area. Founded in 1991 by five artists as a workspace, GSS now supports the performing, rehearsing and teaching needs of a diverse group of individuals and companies. With two studios and 125-seat black box studio/theatre, GSS is a purpose-built dance facility in a dynamic urban setting, one that offers dancers what they need to be successful. The Studio has grown from a cooperatively-run space to a dance and movement arts center managed by an active board of Trustees, a professional staff and volunteers committed to providing affordable facilities for training, rehearsals, and performances. GSS is now home to hundreds of dancers who rehearse and study, and over 20 teachers in a range of disciplines. Green Street Studios is the home of Boston Percussive Dance.', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2334', '', '', '2012-07-08 04:07:00', '2012-07-08 04:07:00', '', 47, 'http://greenstreetstudios.smalls.cc/2012/07/08/2334/', 51, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
