(19, 1, '2012-06-05 02:09:38', '2012-06-05 02:09:38', '<em><strong>FULL SERVICE REAL ESTATE BROKERAGE</strong></em>\n\nForge Realty represents home buyers throughout Massachusetts, providing real estate services and legal advice (through our law offices) at no cost to our clients. As a buyer’s representative, our fee is generated from the commission paid by the seller, so, you pay NOTHING for legal service and advice. You receive professional real estate service and sound legal advice from offer to closing, without spending any more than you would if you handled the transaction without an attorney. Having an attorney at hand can save you valuable time and money, as well as assistance in navigating common issues and pitfalls associated with the purchase process. Our brokers, agents and attorneys will be on your side throughout the process.  With our brokers, attorneys, and affiliate services, we can handle all of your real estate needs, including:\n<ul>\n	<li>Home buyer Brokerage Services</li>\n	<li>Legal Services associated with your purchase</li>\n	<li>Foreclosure and Short sale prospecting</li>\n	<li>Property Management</li>\n	<li>Contractor services</li>\n	<li>Mortgage services</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;', 'For Buyers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'for-buyers', '', '', '2012-06-05 02:09:38', '2012-06-05 02:09:38', '', 0, 'http://forgerealty.smalls.cc/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
