(9, 1, '2012-06-23 16:11:36', '2012-06-23 16:11:36', '<div class = ''post-excerpt'' >\r\nSmallTech offers a number of solutions for building, and managing your image online.\r\n\r\n<h4>	Project Management	</h4>\r\nProject management best suits the needs of a business, that wants to completely rebrand their online presence, or launch a signficantly important new feature, or product. Project management candidates often require launching a new, or redesigned web domain, and developing a mobile application.\r\n\r\n<h4>	Support Contracts	</h4>\r\nOnce the project has launched, it will require ongoing support. While it may fulfill its originally stated goal, business needs evolve. Customers may request new features, new content, and UI alterations. Software, and web sites that we publish online are living documents, that must be monitored, and respond to the changing business climate.\r\n\r\n<h4>	Hourly Contracting	</h4>\r\nSome times the business need has a known start, and end. It is not continuous enough to justify a support contract, but not not large enough to justify full project management. In this case SmallTech offers hourly contracting rates to fulfill your need for your small project.\r\n</div>', 'Cost Structure', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'structure', '', '', '2012-08-02 21:06:51', '2012-08-02 21:06:51', '', 2, 'http://smalls.cc/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
