(11, 1, '2012-06-23 16:12:20', '2012-06-23 16:12:20', '<h2>	Support Contracts	</h2>\r\nOnce the project has launched, it will require ongoing support. While it may fulfill its originally stated goal, business needs evolve. Customers may request new features, new content, and UI alterations. Software, and web sites that we publish online are living documents, that must be monitored, and respond to the changing business climate.\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\nOutsourcing a support contract offers significant cost savings versus direct employment of a skilled technician, especially for smaller businesses with fewer technical needs. However it also provides the chance to address your online needs right away rather than ignoring them, and forgoing the opportunity cost of operating at your greatest efficiency.\r\n\r\n<div	class	=	''page-division''	>\r\n	<h4>	Web Development	</h4>\r\n	The first step toward a turning page views into client interaction is having an attractive, and lean web site for your users to land on. As the your audience matures, and grows, so must your site. The means maintaining up the the display as we add new content to maximize its visual appeal. This also means keeping up with the latest web practices to deliver cleaner, faster, more coherent content for readers, and web browsers.\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n<li><span></span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	> Pages</span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	> Cost </span>\r\n		<li><span	class	=	''type''	>	Small </span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	>	1 - 20	</span><span>	$200 monthly	</span></li>\r\n		<li><span	class	=	''type''	>	Midsize	</span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	>	21 - 500 	</span><span>	$1000 monthly	</span></li>\r\n		<li><span	class	=	''type''	>	Large	</span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	>	500+	</span><span>	$3000 monthly	</span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div	class	=	''page-division''	>\r\n	<h4>	Remote Technical Support	</h4>\r\n	The back bone of any business is delivering an excellent product at market rates, the muscle is the people on your team, and your work stations are your tools. You can do a job with just the right product, right people, but it is exceptionally easier with the right tools. SmallTech works with you to keep all of your technology functioning smoothly, and inutuively so that your people can make the most of every work day.\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n<li><span></span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	> Work Stations </span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	> Cost </span></li>\r\n		<li><span	class	=	''type''	>	Small	</span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	>	1 - 5	</span><span>	$200 monthly	</span></li>\r\n		<li><span	class	=	''type''	>	Midsize	</span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	>	6 - 15	</span><span>	$1000 monthly	</span></li>\r\n		<li><span	class	=	''type''	>	External </span><span	style	=	''text-align:	center;''	>		</span><span>	$5000 monthly	</span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!--<div	class	=	''page-division''	>\r\n	<h4>	Online Marketing </h4>\r\n</div>-->\r\n', 'Support Contracts', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'support-contracts', '', '', '2012-08-09 16:18:04', '2012-08-09 16:18:04', '', 9, 'http://smalls.cc/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
