(203, 1, '2012-07-20 04:39:01', '2012-07-20 04:39:01', '<p>The marketing strategy for any modern company begins, and ends on the web. Your web presence is the first resource that your customers consult before buying from your business. They will use it to find every thing from your business hours, and contact information to details of your products, and services offered. Your online presences extends beyond the site under your control though: ratings sites like Yelp, local news articles, social media outlets all also turn up in search results for your brand. While the basis of a strong company will always be an excellent product, the next element is a coherent web presence: memorable URL, thoughtful content, and well managed third party references.</p>', 'Web', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '25-revision-11', '', '', '2012-07-20 04:39:01', '2012-07-20 04:39:01', '', 25, 'http://smalls.cc/2012/07/20/25-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
