(206, 1, '2012-08-01 16:51:46', '2012-08-01 16:51:46', 'SmallTech offers a number of solutions for building, and managing your image online.\r\n\r\n<h4	Project Management	</h4>\r\nLarge project management best suits the needs of a business, that wants to completely rebrand their online presence, or launch a signficantly important new feature, or product. Project management candidates often require launching a new, or redesigned web domain, and developing a mobile application.\r\n\r\n<h4>	Support Contracts	</h4>\r\nOnce the project has launched, it will require ongoing support. While it may fulfill its originally stated goal, business needs evolve. Customers may request new features, new content, and UI alterations. Software, and web sites that we publish online are living documents, that must be monitored, and respond to the changing business climate. \r\n\r\n<h4	Hourly Contracting	</h4>', 'Cost Structure', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '9-revision-11', '', '', '2012-08-01 16:51:46', '2012-08-01 16:51:46', '', 9, 'http://smalls.cc/2012/08/01/9-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
